snippet: Rebels of Al Qaeda’s Syrian affiliate and other radical Islamic factions launched an assault on Wednesday on a government intelligence building in the northern city of Aleppo, blowing up part of it, two activist groups said.
abstract: Militants in Nursa Front branch of Al Qaeda and other radical Islamists blow up section of Air Force Intelligence building in Aleppo, Syria
lead_paragraph: Rebels of Al Qaeda’s Syrian affiliate and other radical Islamic factions launched an assault on Wednesday on a government intelligence building in the northern city of Aleppo, blowing up part of it, two activist groups said.
